<A>__{here follows a quick montage (presently to be worked out) of no more than four or five images in which the president, by means of cartoons, editorials, headlines (all faithfully reproduced from period yellow journalism) is violently attacked. the montage ends on the word treason. the music cuts. a hand reaches in a side pocket which contains a newspaper recognizably the "enquirer." the hand removes a gun. the gun is shot. many arms seize the hand which is pulled up gun still firing. as the arm is raised in the air, we see that the other arms holding the arm and struggling with it are uniformed, and we see the white house beyond.}
